      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRUISIN' GRAE (1) hit the ground running from out wide with a fast early sectional but run over late and missed the frame when a 2.25 lengths fourth (22.31) over 390m at this track. Can bounce back. LEKTRA AELA (6) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (22.41) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including three wins. Can figure in the finish. PAW TRINNY (7) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten half a length (22.34) behind Tinker Dot at Ballarat. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature. GAPING MARGIN (2) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
